<a name="q1"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>How do I search for positions?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">There are three ways to search for positions:<br><br>
<ul>
    <li>Social Job Matcher allows Bank of America Merrill Lynch job seekers to customize their job search by logging on through Facebook or LinkedIn. Visit the <a href="http://careers.bankofamerica.com/careershome.aspx" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';">Career site homepage</a> and hover over the LinkedIn or Facebook icons and you will be given the option to log in using LinkedIn or Facebook. Using matching technology we'll display potential job opportunities matched from your social media profile (skills, work history, location).<br><br></li>
    <li>On the <a href="http://careers.bankofamerica.com/careershome.aspx" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';">Career site homepage</a>, enter a job title or job area within the <b>Search Jobs</b> box in the upper left-hand corner of the page. The system will automatically begin populating potential jobs that fit the criteria.<br><br></li>
    <li>On the <a href="http://careers.bankofamerica.com/careershome.aspx" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';">Career site homepage</a>, select the <b>Advanced Search</b> button. Select the applicable country and click <b>Begin</b>. Enter your search criteria and click <b>Begin Search.</b> You will be presented with opportunities that match your criteria. To view each position's description, click on the position's title. Note: If nothing is returned when you perform this search, no current vacancies exist in your preferred geographic location and/or within your chosen field of expertise.</li>  
</ul>
</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

