<a name="q4"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>I am interested in opportunities in the U.S., how do I create a career profile?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">On the <a href="http://careers.bankofamerica.com/overview/manage_your_profile.asp" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;">profile page</a>, click on the <b>Create a New Account</b> button located beneath the Sign In information. Follow all of the required steps to successfully create your career profile. You will then be ready to search for positions.</p>
