<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q14"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Will I be considered for other positions when applying for a specific position?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Yes, both your candidate profile and resume will be stored in our database and will be available to our Staffing partners to be considered for alternative vacancies.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q15"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>How often can I update my profile?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">If you are located within the U.S., once you have established a profile on our site, you are able to access your profile at any time. If there is a change in your skills or employment history, you can log in and click on the <b>Access My Profile</b> link to make updates.<br><br>
<b>If you are located outside of the U.S.,</b> visit the <a href="http://ig12.i-grasp.com/fe/tpl_bankofamerica06.asp?s=incYnAPdKpDQcTrFqhVsIvgXzJskCj&amp;key=13778084&amp;c=985157342123&amp;pagestamp=dbmqtdutfuevrfnybl" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';">Update My Details page</a> and then log into your existing profile and update your information.
</p>
