<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q16"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>What happens to my resume after it has been submitted?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Once submitted, your resume enters our candidate tracking system. This tool provides us with a centralized talent pool and serves as the first stop for our Staffing partners, who are trying to identify candidates for specific job openings.</p>
